title: AmmA &mdash; Down where the lilies blow (2012)
description:
AmmA is an experimental folk band from the Netherlands: Once upon a time there were a blonde, a brunette and a redhead who started making music together and discovered that they not only shared their love for folk music, but also that they could collaborate very well.

Check their website at http://www.ammafolk.nl and don't forget to buy and support them in lives if you like this.
